# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

Validator/secrets/*
**/config.yaml
**/config.back.yaml
**webhooks.db*
**.db
**schema.sql
**govdao copy.go.back
**backup.sh
**restore.sh
**.csv
**.tar.gz
**config_docker.yaml
**deploy-preprod.sh
.claude/**
CLAUDE.md
CODEX.md
.claudeignore
backend/db/backup**
backend/migrate-sqlite-to-postgres
feat/feat-page-admin.md
panel/node_modules
panel/dist
panel/.env

# Local environment files (compose secrets, e.g. POSTGRES_PASSWORD).
# Keep .env.example tracked.
.env
**/.env
!.env.example
!**/.env.example

# gnoland-test/ local devnet: .env only holds P2P seed addresses (not a
# secret), and .gnokey-dev/ is a throwaway dev keybase committed for
# reproducibility. Both are exceptions to the rules above.
!gnoland-test/.env
!gnoland-test/.gnokey-dev/
!gnoland-test/.gnokey-dev/**
